videos.headline: Wide-open Gainwell scores on pass from White
videos.description: A wide-open Kenneth Gainwell catches the pass out of the backfield and wins a foot race to the end zone to score for the Tigers.

videos.headline: White hits Austin in stride for the Tigers TD
